query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mc t mk) NoMergeJoin(mc mk t ci) NoMergeJoin(ci mc mk t mi) */ select count(*)
from movie_companies AS mc
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.company_id = 22956 AND t.production_year > 2010
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.role_id = 2
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info_type_id = 16;
